products.name: Demin Dog Coat with Patches
products.description: Denim dog coat with a super soft navy fleece lining.  The coat fastens with long strips of velcro to ensure a very flexible fit. The coat comes with 2 sew on patches and a length of trim so that you can customise the coat yourself. Available in 2 sizes. Small: 50 cm Velcro strap. 28 cm length from collar to rear. 30 cm wide. Neck is approximately 34 cm. Medium: 58 cm Velcro strap. 36 cm length from collar to rear. 36 cm wide. Neck is approximately 50 cm.
products.care: Fully machine washable, but check any additional patches and trim that you sew on for washing instructions.

products.name: Frisco Boulder Plaid Insulated Dog Puffer Coat
products.description: Taking in that crisp mountain air? When the weather gets a tad chilly, it’s the perfect time to head outside! Inspired by a city that embraces the outdoors, this lightweight puffer coat is designed to keep your pal warm so you can explore together. A soft fleece lining provides a comfy layer of warmth for cooler temperatures, and the water-resistant exterior and covered leash hole adds a layer of protection for all your walks. That’s the function, now for the fashion—the V-shaped plaid look is so chic this season.
products.care: Fully machine washable, but check sew on for washing instructions.

products.name: Frisco Portland Insulated Dog Parka
products.description: Keep your furry hipster warm all winter without compromising on style. This pet parka is designed to protect your pet from chilly weather while keeping it chill. It’s designed with a comfy plush lining to turn up the cozy and a detachable faux fur-lined hood for that wintry glam. A midrise collar provides more coverage for your pet’s neck area from chilly conditions. The outer shell is water-resistant to protect from rain and light snow, and comes in trendy, satiny colors. Plus, it has a covered leash hole so you can easily access a collar underneath the parka.
products.care: Fully machine washable, but check sew on for washing instructions.

products.name: Frisco Reflective Water-Resistant Insulated Dog Coat
products.description: This coat is guaranteed to bring high quality, cold weather comfort to your companion’s wardrobe. This puffy coat is made with a water-resistant polyester shell with reflective accents to keep your pet dry and stylish. With this wardrobe must-have, the winter forecast is cute and cozy.
products.care: Fully machine washable, but check sew on for washing instructions.

products.name: Frisco Rainy Days Dog Raincoat
products.description: Remember to measure your pet for the paw-fect fit. Rain or shine, always be ready to go with the Frisco Dog Rainy Days Raincoat. This doggy raincoat is made with a water-resistant PVC coating designed to keep your pup dry come drizzle or downpour, and it has secure neck and belly fuzzy fastener straps to ensure a snug fit all around—and a drier pooch. The built-in leash hole lets you attach a leash to a collar worn underneath the raincoat, so you can always be ready to dash, and the large reflective stripes help increase visibility for added safety. Plus, it’s available in different sizes to fit pups of most proportions
products.care: Fully machine washable, but check sew on for washing instructions.
